-### 1.1 用戶登入
-```http
-POST /auth/login
-```
-
-**Request Body:**
-```json
-{
-  "username": "nurse",
-  "password": "nurse123"
-}
-```
-
-**Response (200):**
-```json
-{
-  "success": true,
-  "data": {
-    "user": {
-      "id": "usr_001",
