-```
-
-**Response (200):**
-```json
-{
-  "success": true,
-  "message": "登出成功"
-}
-```
-
-### 1.3 刷新 Token
-```http
-POST /auth/refresh
-```
-
-**Request Body:**
-```json
-{
-  "refreshToken": "refresh_token_here"
